org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.kafka.internals

类 Kafka08Fetcher<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.kafka.internals.AbstractFetcher<T,kafka.common.TopicAndPartition>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.kafka.internals.Kafka08Fetcher<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of elements produced by the fetcher.

    public class Kafka08Fetcher<T>
extends AbstractFetcher<T,kafka.common.TopicAndPartition>
    A fetcher that fetches data from Kafka brokers via the Kafka 0.8 low-level consumer API. The fetcher also handles the explicit communication with ZooKeeper to fetch initial offsets and to write offsets to ZooKeeper.

      • findLeaderForPartitions

        private static java.util.Map<org.apache.kafka.common.Node,java.util.List<KafkaTopicPartitionState<kafka.common.TopicAndPartition>>> findLeaderForPartitions(java.util.List<KafkaTopicPartitionState<kafka.common.TopicAndPartition>> partitionsToAssign,
                                                                                                                                                            java.util.Properties kafkaProperties)
                                                                                                                                                     throws java.lang.Exception
        Find leaders for the partitions.

        From a high level, the method does the following: - Get a list of FetchPartitions (usually only a few partitions) - Get the list of topics from the FetchPartitions list and request the partitions for the topics. (Kafka doesn't support getting leaders for a set of partitions) - Build a Map<Leader, List<FetchPartition>> where only the requested partitions are contained.

        参数:
        partitionsToAssign - fetch partitions list
        返回:
        leader to partitions map
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception

      • getInvalidOffsetBehavior

        private static long getInvalidOffsetBehavior(java.util.Properties config)
        Retrieve the behaviour of "auto.offset.reset" from the config properties. A partition needs to fallback to "auto.offset.reset" as default offset when we can't find offsets in ZK to start from in StartupMode.GROUP_OFFSETS startup mode.
        参数:
        config - kafka consumer properties
        返回:
        either OffsetRequest.LatestTime() or OffsetRequest.EarliestTime()
